      <title>哈萨克斯坦结束最长宽松周期，着眼于价格压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/kazakhstan-ends-longest-easing-cycle-with-eye-on-price-pressures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈萨克斯坦停止了近十年来最长的一系列降息，在央行评估国内和邻国俄罗斯的价格压力之际，控制了借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/kazakhstan-ends-longest-easing-cycle-with-eye-on-price-pressures</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 07:05:07 GMT</pubDate>
