    <item>
      <title>日本央行押注日本五年期国债收益率升至2011年以来最高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/japan-s-five-year-yield-rises-to-highest-since-2011-on-boj-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本五年期国债收益率攀升至 2011 年以来的最高水平，原因是越来越多的人猜测日本央行将加息以遏制日元疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/japan-s-five-year-yield-rises-to-highest-since-2011-on-boj-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 06:34:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯托纳拉斯表示，欧洲央行是时候与美联储分道扬镳了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/it-s-time-for-the-ecb-to-diverge-from-the-fed-stournaras-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行理事会成员雅尼斯·斯图尔纳拉斯表示，欧洲央行不应该害怕改变其“过度审慎”的利率立场，偏离美联储的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/it-s-time-for-the-ecb-to-diverge-from-the-fed-stournaras-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 06:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东风险刺激需求，金价创历史新高，白银飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/gold-hits-fresh-high-as-mideast-tensions-boost-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于以色列为伊朗可能发动的袭击做准备，提振了避险需求，且交易员权衡了美国货币政策的前景，黄金价格上涨至创纪录水平，白银价格创下三年多以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/gold-hits-fresh-high-as-mideast-tensions-boost-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 02:26:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着市场情绪的转变，铁矿石价格创两年来最佳一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/iron-ore-heads-for-10-weekly-surge-as-china-outlook-improves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场猜测中国经济可能正在好转，铁矿石价格迎来两年来最好的一周，提振了需求前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/iron-ore-heads-for-10-weekly-surge-as-china-outlook-improves</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 02:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
